<Layout title="About | Squigi’s Pizza of Griffith">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">About Squigi’s</h1>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-lg">
      <p>
        Squigi’s Pizza of Griffith is a family-owned pizzeria proudly serving the
        Griffith community with classic pizza and Italian favorites.
      </p>

      <p>
        From our fresh dough and house sauce to our friendly, hometown service,
        we believe great food brings people together.
      </p>

      <p>
        Join us for dine-in, carryout, or delivery — and thank you for supporting
        local.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
